{"tid":2286832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貿發局明與協辦機構開會　商討書展是否可下月中舉行","createTime":"2020-11-15T09:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T10:49:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6c079a73a6fb8d2157d0107257ad97da79c23f","tid":2286832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560075-20201115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560075-20201115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a656008a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560075-20201115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9f2b5537\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560075-20201115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n貿易發展局副總裁周啟良表示，明日會與9個書展協辦機構開會，商討書展能否如期於12月中舉行的問題。<br />\n<br />\n周啟良出席一個電台節目後說，過去數月有關書展的準備工作，進行得如火如荼，有8成、超過600個展商已報名參展。但因應疫情變化及政府收緊防疫措施，要再與業界商討，他初步希望可延遲作最終決定的時間。<br />\n<br />\n今年的香港書展，原定於7月15至21日舉行，但因當時本港爆發第三波疫情而要延期，之後公布延至今年12月16日至22日舉行。"},{"pid":"c2921381250b8e69832e56f064f997f1265bbbd7","tid":2286832,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"書商邊會估到政府過左半年都搞唔掂既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1e3da1d53eae9a18afd61530955ce52edf9b49","tid":2286832,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"問過中聯辦未？"},{"pid":"b2f8b3933c2d9b61a207ff94e8f4f99ba4687d8e","tid":2286832,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"等到下年5月攪一次7月再攪一次書展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset